          <li><a href="corp-demo.html">Book a Demo</a></li>
        </ul></div>
      <div><p class="footer__col-title">Company</p><ul class="footer__links">
        <li><a href="about.html">About Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="science.html">The Science</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">GDPR &amp; Data</a></li>
      </ul></div>
      <div><p class="footer__col-title">Get Started</p><ul class="footer__links">
        <li><a href="corp-demo.html">Book a Demo</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://online.vyvehealth.co.uk">Member Portal</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:team@vyvehealth.co.uk">Contact Us</a></li>
      </ul></div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer__bottom">
      <p class="footer__copy">© 2026 VYVE Health Ltd. All rights reserved. Registered in England &amp; Wales.</p>
      <div class="footer__badges">
        <span class="footer__badge">GDPR Compliant</span>
        <span class="footer__badge">UK Data</span>
